title: Alex Strand
link_one: A reactjs/express app that gives you a random submission from r/dailyprogrammer
link_two: Pulls data from a json file that then constructs this static site, using Rust
link_three: An android app that pulls data from json files, for all patterns in ITF Taekwondo
content: My name is Alex Strand and I am currently working as a web developer. I play trombone, guitar and also practice Taekwondo. Currently I'm into React JS, Styled Components,and Redux(on the front end) and Java/Kotlin(for android) and Rust on the backend.
